arts.ttl: Crystal Palace vs Fredrikstad preview: UEFA Conference League Qualifying Round, 1st Leg, 2025
arts.sum: For the first time since 1998, Crystal Palace will take part in a competitive European fixture as they host Fredrikstad at Selhurst Park, with the goal of qualifying for the UEFA Conference League group stage. For Eze in particular, this is likely to be his final game in Crystal Palace colours as he sits on the brink of a move to North London.
